Package SpaceShooters.Ship

Class PlayerShipData

java.lang.Object
SpaceShooters.Ship.PlayerShipData
public class PlayerShipData extends Object
Represents data associated with a player-controlled ship, including crew, cannon, shield, and ship levels. Made for JSON serialization and deserialization.
